Description: Implements statistical tests, goodness-of-fit diagnostics, and topic-number selection     tools for multiple topic-model implementations, including Latent Dirichlet Allocation and related     estimators. The package follows the optimal topic identification approach of Lewis and Grossetti     (2022) <https://jmlr.org/papers/v23/19-297.html>.
